ve, high-performance vibe worthy of the GT-R name.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"972\" data-end=\"1227\"\u003eFeaturing the car’s wide-body stance, massive rear wing, and aggressive exhaust layout, this piece celebrates one of the most feared machines in the automotive world. Perfect for gaming rooms, desk setups, studios, garages, and any car lover’s collection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1229\" data-end=\"1374\"\u003ePrinted across multiple panels for a wide, impactful display, this poster stands out as both art and tribute to the legend known as \u003cstrong data-start=\"1361\" data-end=\"1373\"\u003eGodzilla\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394461434152,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394461466920,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394461499688,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/NissanSkylineGOZILLACarSet3PieceSet_2.webp?v=1765027283"},{"product_id":"fortuner-x-build-to-dominate-car-set-3-piece-set","title":"FORTUNER x Build to Dominate | Car Set | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"107\" data-end=\"261\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"107\" data-end=\"189\"\u003ePremium high-definition wall poster of TOYOTA FORTUNER | Car Set | 3-Piece Set\u003c\/strong\u003e, designed to instantly elevate the power and premium vibe of your room.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"484\"\u003ePrinted on ultra-thick \u003cstrong data-start=\"286\" data-end=\"315\"\u003e300 GSM matte photo paper\u003c\/strong\u003e for deep colours, razor-sharp detailing, and a smooth anti-glare finish. Durable, fade-resistant, and crafted to deliver a bold, premium wall presence with zero effort.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"486\" data-end=\"767\"\u003eThis