acher-the-red-legend-formula-1-3-piece-set","title":"Michael Schumacher | The Red Legend | Formula 1 | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eA tribute to one of the greatest Formula 1 drivers in history — Michael Schumacher.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis striking motorsport artwork captures Schumacher during his iconic Ferrari era, celebrating the passion, precision, and dominance that defined an entire generation of Formula 1 racing. Featuring bold typography, championship-winning Ferrari imagery, and a clean editorial-style composition, this poster honors the legacy of a true racing legend.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProduct Details:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePrinted on 300 GSM premium matte sheet\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHigh-resolution Formula 1 artwork\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFerrari-inspired racing aesthetics\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eModern editorial poster design\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFrame not included\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePerfect For:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFormula 1 fans\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFerrari enthusiasts\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMotorsport collectors\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGaming and workstation setups\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRacing-themed wall decor\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAbout Michael Schumacher:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMichael Schumacher is regarded as one of the most successful Formula 1 drivers of all time. With seven World Championship titles and an era-defining partnership with Ferrari, he transformed the sport through relentless dedication, exceptional racecraft, and unmatched consistency. His influence continues to inspire generations of drivers and motorsport fans worldwide.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNote:\u003c\/strong\u003e Slight color variation may occur due to lighting and screen differences.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51947317494056,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51947317526824,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51947317559592,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/MichaelSchumacherTheRedLegendFormula13PieceSet_1.jpg?v=1780633569"},{"product_id":"let-the-storm-begin-formula-1-3-piece-set","title":"Let The Storm Begin | Formula 1 | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eA powerful tribute to Max Verstappen's relentless speed, aggression, and championship-winning mindset.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis dynamic Formula 1 artwork showcases Verstappen's Red Bull Racing machine emerging through stormy skies, capturing the intensity, precision, and dominance that have defined a new era of motorsport. The bold vertical composition, dramatic atmosphere, and modern typography create a striking centerpiece for any racing enthusiast's collection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProduct Details:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePrinted on 300 GSM premium matte sheet\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHigh-resolution Formula 1 artwork\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRed Bull Racing inspired design\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePremium vertical poster layout\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFrame not included\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePerfect For:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFormula 1 fans\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMax Verstappen